Genetic Algorithms. 

Explanation: The paper discusses the use of Genetic Algorithms (GA) and proposes a mechanism called Dynamic Parameter Encoding (DPE) to improve the efficiency and precision of GA. The paper also explores the problem of premature convergence in GAs through two convergence models. There is no mention of other sub-categories of AI such as Case Based, Neural Networks, Probabilistic Methods, Reinforcement Learning, Rule Learning, or Theory.
